Description_lang: Restorative waters wash over a friendly target, healing them for $s1 and an additional $o2 over $d.

description_blz.en_US: Restorative waters wash over a friendly target, healing them for 14,818 and an additional 8,071 over 18 sec.

description_blz.zh_TW: 以療癒之水洗滌友方目標，為其治療14,369點生命力，並在18秒內，額外恢復8,071點生命力。
